{
  "stem": "11174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was the big thing in the town like a rodeo, [LAUGHS] let's say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was the big thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I think I mentioned it before, that there was no officially address because just the name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The mailman knew everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one day a guy came and he wanted to make probably a few zlotys so he made up little streets and, and, and came in and gave us-- we had to-- paid him a zloty, a little, and it said a street with a number.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH] with number two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was built with wood, a wooden house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few rooms only.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had large kitchen, a dining room, living room-- no, the kitchen was dining room living-- dining room and kitchen, and the other room was dining room, living room, and my father's [NON-ENGLISH] room, that as the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And was all-- at night there was a little bedroom and there was another room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was the sukkah for Sukkos and also whatever was needed was used in other room, another large room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were six children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was the rabbi in town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were considered better than the-- than, than the middle class.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, telephone-- there wasn't a post office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If somebody wanted to call you from another town, it was called a visa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they will call to the post office and the post office send them a messenger with a little slip.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was called-- I don't know what it's was called-- a visa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they let you know and what time you should come to the post office.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
